{"type": "article", "id": 23830, "title": "极简主义设计为何如此迷人，这本书试图给出答案", "description": "如果你对这本书感兴趣，可以去美国亚马逊上购买。", "date": "2016-03-14T13:03:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 24862, "name": "极简风"}, {"id": 7417, "name": "出版物"}, {"id": 19383, "name": "书籍"}, {"id": 4199, "name": "海报"}, {"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 24863, "name": "Thames & Hudson"}, {"id": 24864, "name": "Transmission"}, {"id": 24865, "name": "Stuart Tolley"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 435, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134552K86Dp0eHMY5sPJVB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>“极简”的设计其实并不简单。过去两年里，平面设计师 Stuart Tolley 一直在研究极简主义的平面设计。最近，他将这些研究成果集结，并在 <a href=\"http://www.thamesandhudson.com/Min/9780500292198\">Thames &amp; Hudson</a> 出版了一本书，名叫《<a href=\"http://www.transmission.design/work/min-thames-hudson/\">MIN: The New Simplicity in Graphic Design</a>》，这本书介绍了极简主义的设计历史和方法。</p>\n<p>先来认识一下 Stuart Tolley 吧。他是平面设计事务所 <a href=\"http://www.transmission.design/\">Transmission</a> 的创始人，这是一家挺小的平面设计公司，总共只有三人——除了 Stuart Tolley 外，还有两名平面设计师，分别是 Matthew Lee 和 Julia Zaltzman。</p>\n<p>公司虽小，他们的客户范围却很广，包括初创企业，也有大的国际品牌，让我们先来看看他们过去的作品：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134543vcW604xVI5SXknej.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"> Transmission 工作室的作品集合 </figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134544ZoADyw205JN4hSEQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">这是他们为 Sci-Fi-London Film Festival  设计的宣传册</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134545WCOwex5iGYJo6h78.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">为 Sci-Fi-London Film Festival  设计的海报</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021345463PVvd8DEtmXir21U.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Sci-Fi-London Film Festival </figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134546mD93t1vNYefl7FM4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">这是他们的另一个作品，是为 Quarto Publishing 设计的书籍</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134547B10WYryp8XNwljH5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">为 Quarto Publishing 设计的书籍</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134547YJkEdr2shRCxqluP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">这是工作室为 Unlimited Gallery 展览设计的宣传单</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134548uLSRPDHFEs46qMI5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">这是工作室为  Self Initiated 设计的宣传单</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021345485mrAnoKwPItDYxyq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">细节很精致啊，配色也不错</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134549QfE9P2u5IeJti7Gy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">这些平面作品都能在他们官方网站上买到</figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">以上这些作品多少有点儿“极简风”，在探讨极简的书籍中，Stuart Tolley 也提及，“我花了很长时间去搜集极简主义的案例，也很享受这个过程。我很好奇，极简主义为什么有一种强烈的吸引力。”</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134549GO6ECy5R0PvB8H1a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68370166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">这就是 Stuart Tolley 的新书 《MIN: The New Simplicity in Graphic Design》了</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134550KocIJYjh2yODQNXg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68370166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">书籍封面</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134550nbz3QEVJaSikj0dm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68370166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">书籍内页图，书中介绍了不少极简主义的案例</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134551wfOyYXKg1Z8GpLQj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68370166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">内页图</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134551hw8NzWd6uDHRVmSb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68370166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>举个例子，在追溯极简主义的历史时，Stuart Tolley 介绍了建筑师卡尔·安德烈（Carl Andre）。卡尔是美国当代艺术家，也是极简主义的代表人物之一，他使用一些不用雕刻的素材来呈现建筑的形态。卡尔常说，“如果要切割素材，不如把它们直接拿来切割空间。”卡尔用一系列石砖作品重新定义了雕塑。Stuart Tolley 就是从卡尔·安德烈入手，介绍了极简主义的历史的。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134551C0smIBAPrYb2ctaN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Carl Andre 的艺术作品</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134552BVraUKJfiNlzvT6d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75085324\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Carl Andre 的作品</figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">如果你对这本书感兴趣，可以去<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Min-New-Simplicity-Graphic-Design/dp/0500292191/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1457926496&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=MIN%3A+The+New+Simplicity+in+Graphic+Design\">美国亚马逊</a>上购买。</p>\n<p>题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/minimalism-graphic-design-stuart-tolley-100316\">itsnicethat</a></p>\n\n"}